   "source": [
    "n = 12\n",
    "t = range(-1,stop=1,length=n+1)\n",
    "y = @. t^2 + t + 0.5*sin(20*t)\n",
    "\n",
    "using Plots\n",
    "scatter(t,y,label=\"data\",leg=:top)"
   ]

    "p = LinearInterpolation(t,y)\n",

   ]
